paragraphs.title: 2. queryMetrics: Get Query execution times
paragraphs.text:
case class Query(
    queryId: String,
    runId: Long,
    startTime: Long,
    endTime:Long,
    executionTimeMs: Long,
    queryResultValidationSuccess: Boolean
    )
    
val queryMetrics = spark.read.option("basePath", queryMetricsPath).json(s"${queryMetricsPath}/*/**")
val query = queryMetrics.select(
    $"queryId",
    $"runId",
    $"queryResultValidationSuccess",
    $"runtimes.startTime".alias("startTime"),
    $"runTimes.endTime".alias("endTime"),
    $"runTimes.executionTimeMs".alias("executionTimeMs")
    ).as[Query]
    
queryMetrics.show(5)

query.createOrReplaceTempView("query")

paragraphs.title: 3.1 Spark Events: Task details
paragraphs.text:
case class Task(
    queryId: String,
    runId: Long,
    taskId: Long,
    taskAttemptId: Long,
    stageId: Long,
    stageAttemptId: Long,
    executorId: String,
    host: String,
    startTime: Long,
    finishTime: Long,
    killed: Boolean,
    failed: Boolean,
    shuffleBytesWritten: Long,
    shuffleBytesRead: Long,
    jvmGCTime: Long,
    memoryBytesSpilled: Long,
    diskBytesSpilled: Long,
    taskType: String,
    locality: String,
    taskEndReason: String)
    
    
val taskEvents = sparkEvents.filter($"Event" === "SparkListenerTaskEnd").select(
    $"queryId".alias("queryId"),
    $"Task Info.Task ID".alias("taskId"),
    $"Task Info.Attempt"alias("taskAttemptId"),
    $"Stage ID".alias("stageId"),
    $"Stage Attempt ID".alias("stageAttemptId"),
    $"Task Info.Executor ID".alias("executorId"),
    $"Task Info.Host".alias("host"),
    $"Task Info.Launch Time".alias("startTime"),
    $"Task Info.Finish Time".alias("finishTime"),
    $"Task Info.Killed".alias("killed"),
    $"Task Info.Failed".alias("failed"),
    $"Task Metrics.Shuffle Write Metrics.Shuffle Bytes Written".alias("shuffleBytesWritten"),
    ($"Task Metrics.Shuffle Read Metrics.Remote Bytes Read" + $"Task Metrics.Shuffle Read Metrics.Local Bytes Read").alias("shuffleBytesRead"),
    
    
    $"Task Metrics.JVM GC Time".alias("jvmGCTime"),
    $"Task Metrics.Memory Bytes Spilled".alias("memoryBytesSpilled"),
    $"Task Metrics.Disk Bytes Spilled".alias("diskBytesSpilled") , 
    $"Task Type".alias("taskType"),
    $"Task Info.Locality".alias("locality"),
    $"Task End Reason".alias("taskEndReason"))
 
 
val task = taskEvents.as("t").join(query.as("q"), query("queryId") === taskEvents("queryId") &&  query("startTime") < taskEvents("startTime") && query("endTime") > taskEvents("finishTime")).select("t.*", "q.runId").as[Task]

task.createOrReplaceTempView("task")

paragraphs.text:
%sql
with totalTasks as
(select queryId, runId, count(1) as totalTasks from task group by 1,2 order by 1,2),
successfulTasks as
(select queryId, runId, count(1) as successfulTasks from task where killed = "false" and failed = "false" group by 1,2 order by 1,2)
select tt.queryId, tt.runId, totalTasks-successfulTasks as failedTasks, successfulTasks from totalTasks tt,successfulTasks st where st.queryId = tt.queryId and st.runId = tt.runId

paragraphs.title: 3.2 Spark Events: Stage details
paragraphs.text:
case class Stage(
    queryId: String,
    runId: Long,
    stageId: Long,
    stageAttemptId: Long,
    startTime: Long,
    finishTime: Long,
    totalTasks: Long,
   // totalFailedTasks: Long,
    totalShuffleBytesWritten: Long,
    totalShuffleBytesRead: Long,
    totalInputBytes: Long,
   // totalOutputBytes: Long,
    totalInputRecordsRead: Long,
    totalOutputRecords: Long,
    jvmGCTime: Long
    )

val stagesTemp = sparkEvents.filter($"Event" === "SparkListenerStageCompleted").select(
    $"queryId",
    $"Stage Info.Stage ID".alias("stageId"),
    $"Stage Info.Stage Attempt ID".alias("stageAttemptId"),
    $"Stage Info.Submission Time".alias("startTime"),
    $"Stage Info.Completion Time".alias("finishTime"),
    $"Stage Info.Number of Tasks".alias("totalTasks"),
    $"Stage Info.Accumulables.Value".alias("accumulablesValue"),
    array_position( $"Stage Info.Accumulables.Name", "internal.metrics.shuffle.write.bytesWritten").alias("totalShuffleBytesWrittenIndex"),
    array_position( $"Stage Info.Accumulables.Name", "internal.metrics.shuffle.read.localBytesRead").alias("localShuffleBytesReadIndex"),
    array_position( $"Stage Info.Accumulables.Name", "internal.metrics.shuffle.read.remoteBytesRead").alias("remoteShuffleBytesReadIndex"),
    array_position( $"Stage Info.Accumulables.Name", "internal.metrics.input.bytesRead").alias("totalInputBytesIndex"),
    array_position( $"Stage Info.Accumulables.Name", "internal.metrics.input.recordsRead").alias("totalInputRecordsReadIndex"),
    array_position( $"Stage Info.Accumulables.Name", "number of output rows").alias("totalOutputRecordsIndex"),
    array_position( $"Stage Info.Accumulables.Name", "internal.metrics.jvmGCTime").alias("jvmGCTimeIndex"))
    
 val stage = stagesTemp.select(
     $"queryId",
     $"stageId",
     $"stageAttemptId",
     $"startTime",
     $"finishTime",
     $"totalTasks",
     expr("CAST( Case when totalShuffleBytesWrittenIndex = 0 then 0 else element_at(accumulablesValue, CAST(totalShuffleBytesWrittenIndex AS INTEGER)) end AS BIGINT)").alias("totalShuffleBytesWritten"),
     (expr("CAST(Case when localShuffleBytesReadIndex = 0 then 0 else element_at(accumulablesValue, CAST(localShuffleBytesReadIndex AS INTEGER)) end AS BIGINT)") + 
     expr("CAST( Case when remoteShuffleBytesReadIndex = 0 then 0 else element_at(accumulablesValue, CAST(remoteShuffleBytesReadIndex AS INTEGER)) end AS BIGINT)"))
     .alias("totalShuffleBytesRead"),
     expr("CAST( Case when totalInputBytesIndex = 0 then 0 else element_at(accumulablesValue, CAST(totalInputBytesIndex AS INTEGER)) end AS BIGINT)").alias("totalInputBytes"),
     expr("CAST( Case when totalInputRecordsReadIndex = 0 then 0 else element_at(accumulablesValue, CAST(totalInputRecordsReadIndex AS INTEGER)) end AS BIGINT)").alias("totalInputRecordsRead"),
     expr("CAST( Case when totalOutputRecordsIndex = 0 then 0 else element_at(accumulablesValue, CAST(totalOutputRecordsIndex AS INTEGER)) end AS BIGINT)").alias("totalOutputRecords"),
     expr("CAST( Case when jvmGCTimeIndex = 0 then 0 else element_at(accumulablesValue, CAST(jvmGCTimeIndex AS INTEGER)) end AS BIGINT)").alias("jvmGCTime")
 ).as("s").join(query.as("q"), query("queryId") === $"s.queryId" &&  query("startTime") < $"s.startTime" && query("endTime") > $"s.finishTime").select("s.*", "q.runId").as[Stage]
    
 
 stage.createOrReplaceTempView("stage")
